    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Calling all project car enthusiasts and skilled mechanics \u2014 here's your next hands-on adventure! This vehicle is being sold as-is in poor condition, meaning it comes with notable mechanical issues and visible wear that will require attention. The good news? It's a fantastic opportunity to get your hands dirty and bring a car back to life at a budget-friendly price. Perfect for those who love a challenge and have the skills to match!",
      "price": 3500.0,
