    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity for the savvy buyer looking for a project car or basic transportation! We're being upfront with you \u2014 this vehicle is in poor condition and shows significant wear both inside and out. You'll notice visible body damage, a well-worn interior, and some mechanical issues that will need attention. That said, it does still get you from point A to point B, and at this price point, it represents a real chance to own a vehicle without breaking the bank. Perfect for someone handy who doesn't mind rolling up their sleeves!",
